HEADWORD: Fermerere
<hw>Fer"mer*ere</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>enfermerier</ets>, fr. <ets>enfermerie</ets> infirmary. See
<er>Infirmary</er>.]</ety> <def>The officer in a religious house who had
the care of the infirmary.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

